Compare OOPS vs procedural programming


| Feature          | Procedural Programming | OOPS              |
| ---------------- | ---------------------- | ----------------- |
| Main focus       | Functions & steps      | Objects           |
| Data & functions | Separate               | Bound together    |
| Real-life match  | Weak                   | Strong            |
| Code reuse       | Difficult              | Easy              |
| Security         | Low                    | High              |
| Large projects   | Hard to manage         | Easy to manage    |
| Maintenance      | Time-consuming         | Easier            |
| Examples         | C, Pascal              | Java, C++, Python |
